"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:57:57.000Z","msg":"行過入去都知入面死城一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e5583c0d794df2cf960a761724bafa431363f6","tid":974791,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:02:56.000Z","msg":"在過去5年半，有230天用作舉行不同活動，吸引幾百至5萬人次，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴撚線"},{"pid":"05c45d4e158da417ea06ba5c49f4c7f56897cc63","tid":974791,"uid":53384,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:35:50.000Z","msg":"而家郵輪碼頭連交通配套都未完善，郵輪碼頭有郵輪埋岸班遊客就響到等架5R，舊年就多左荷里活廣場派shuttle 接客，但班郵輪客往往就等成幾個鐘就未出到市區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算有的士入郵輪碼頭都唔夠車消化班郵輪客啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反，西九龍高鐵站經已響市區再加埋響柯士甸站隔離，政府都幾條巴士線去港九新界，驚死班強國人去唔到香港每一個角落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港政府仲有無諗住賺鬼佬班中高階班客既錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 眼見呢幾年黎香港既東南亞同埋鬼佬客都少左好多，每日響地鐵聽到就係一大堆充滿住鄉音既蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}